text:
Boston Road, north from Thwaites Place. Intersecting Boston Road is White Plains Road on which appears the elevated structure of the I.R.T. White Plains Road subway line.

1917.

original_title: Bronx: White Plains Road - Thwaites Place
text:
White Plains Road (foreground), at the N.W. corner of Thwaites Place. The two story frame house, on the extreme right, bears No. 2241.

July 28, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.
